# Gradient Background Demo

Output examples/svgs/backgrounds/gradient-background.svg

Set FontSize 16
Set Template macos
Set Theme dracula
Set Background "gradient(#ff6b6b, #4ecdc4:diagonal:reverse)"
Set BackgroundPadding 20

Type "echo 'Hello from a reversed diagonal gradient background!'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Type "This looks pretty cool"
Sleep 1s
